Gets the serialization formatter type used by CSLA .NET
for all explicit object serialization (such as cloning,
n-level undo, etc).

示例定义：
var b = new CompositeBlocks
{
    MainBlock = new Block
    {
        EntityType = typeof(Book),
        BlockType = BlockType.Detail
    },
    Children =
    {
        new ChildBlock{
            ChildrenPropertyNameSetter = Book.ChapterListProperty
        }
    }
};

